    "  3. In SharePoint, click 'Download' (don't download yet)",
    "  4. Open Browser DevTools (F12) → Network tab",
    "  5. Look for 'videomanifest' request and copy the full URL",
    "",
    "Method 2 - From SharePoint:",
    "  1. Navigate to SharePoint with videos",
    "  2. Click on a video to open player",
    "  3. Open DevTools (F12) → Network tab → Refresh",
    "  4. Filter by 'videomanifest' and copy the URL"
